ossible to the right and left is the same, or sheer ignorance of natural/realsitic steering. This is really wrong.Summary:A game that makes your whole creativity appear and caress your eyes at first glance, a pleasant environment, in a 10 minutes will completely destroy the illusion of a good game because of the lack of realism and plenty of mistakes, but since I wrote the first review of the game has changed a LOT better, and it's not the game that I regretted that I bought. however, it needs to have a lot of care.Im giving 6/10Last review i gave 1/10---------------------------------------------------------------Stále hru nedoporučuji, avšak chválím vývojáře za masivní skok dál a věřím že jednou budu moct hru doporučit./I still not recommend the game, however, I praise the developer for a massive jump from the very first alpha stage and i hope that someday I will recommend the game....And sorry for my bad English :< I did not pay attention in school xD"
